{"title_page": "List of original programs distributed by Quibi", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n[[File:Quibi Logo.png|120px|frameless|right]]\n\n'''[[Quibi]]''' is an [[Over-the-top media service|over-the-top]] American short-form streaming platform that generates content for viewing on mobile devices. To capitalize on mobile viewing specifically, Quibi provides \"quick bites\" of content that can be viewed under 10 minutes, and the content utilizes \"Turnstyle\" technology in order dynamically switch between portrait and landscape viewing formats.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ramos |first1=Dino-Ray |title=Quibi\u2019s Tom Conrad Addresses Platform Skepticism And Reinvented Storytelling \u2013 CES |url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/quibi-tom-conrad-short-form-streaming-platform-ces-consumer-electronics-show-jeffrey-katzenberg-meg-whitman-1202823763/ |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=January 8, 2020}}</ref>\n\nQuibi's content falls into three main categories:<ref name=\"/Film-90\">{{cite web |last1=Evangelista |first1=Chris |title=Quibi Offering 90-Day Free Trial For Potential Subscribers |url=https://www.slashfilm.com/quibi-free-trial/ |website=[[/Film]] |date=March 6, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n*Movies in Chapters: Longer features broken into chapters of 7\u201310 minutes\n*Unscripted and Docs: Shows that are episodic in nature and are 10 minutes or less\n*Daily Essentials: Daily curated quick bites of news, entertainment, and inspiration in the 5\u20136 minute range\n\n==Original programming==\n{{Dynamic list}}\n\n===Drama===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n!Category\n! Genre\n! Premiere\n! Notes\n|-\n| ''50 States of Fright''\n| rowspan=\"4\" |Movies in Chapters\n| [[Horror fiction|Horror]]\n| April 6, 2020 <small>(early access)</small><br />April 13, 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/50-states-of-fright-trailer-new/ |title=\u201950 States of Fright\u2019 Trailer: Sam Raimi and Quibi Are Ready to Scare You|work=/Film |date=April 3, 2020|accessdate=April 6, 2020|first=Chris |last=Evangelista}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Donnelly|first1=Matt|title=Jeffrey Katzenberg's Mobile Content Platform Orders Series From Jason Blum, Guillermo del Toro|url=https://variety.com/2018/biz/news/jeffrey-katzenbergs-wndrco-orders-series-from-jason-blum-guillermo-del-toro-1202975458|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=October 10, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n|''Most Dangerous Game''\n|[[Action fiction|Action]] [[Thriller (genre)|thriller]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |April 6, 2020\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Survive''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''When the Streetlights Go On''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|}\n\n===Comedy===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n!Category\n! Genre\n! Premiere\n! Notes\n|-\n| ''[[Flipped (TV series)|Flipped]]''\n|Movies in Chapters\n| [[Comedy]]\n|April 6, 2020\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/will-forte-kaitlin-olson-to-headline-quibi-comedy-series-flipped-eva-longoria-arturo-castro-andy-garcia-also-star-1202702721/|title=Will Forte & Kaitlin Olson To Headline Quibi Comedy Series 'Flipped', Eva Longoria, Arturo Castro & Andy Garcia Also Star|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=August 26, 2019|access-date=2019-09-24}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Nikki Fre$h''\n|Unscripted and Docs\n|\n|April 6, 2020\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|}\n\n===Docu-series===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n!Category\n! Genre\n! Premiere\n! Notes\n|-\n| ''Fierce Queens''\n| rowspan=\"8\" |Unscripted and Docs\n| rowspan=\"8\" |[[Television documentary|Docuseries]]\n| rowspan=\"8\" |April 6, 2020\n|<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC - BBC Studios wins its first Quibi commission \u2013 Fierce Queens (w/t) - Media Centre|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/bbcstudios/2019/bbc-studios-quibi|work=www.bbc.co.uk|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref>\n|-\n|''I Promise''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n|''Memory Hole''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n| ''[[NightGowns with Sasha Velour]]''\n|<ref>{{cite web|last=Rudolph|first=Christopher|title=Get Your First Glimpse of Sasha Velour's New Quibi Series, \"Nightgowns\"|url=http://www.newnownext.com/sasha-velour-nightgowns-quibi/01/2020/|work=[[NewNowNext]]|date=January 9, 2020|access-date=January 12, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Prodigy''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Run This City''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Shape of Pasta''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''&Music''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|}\n\n===Reality, competition, and talk shows===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n!Category\n! Genre\n! Premiere\n! Notes\n|-\n| ''[[Chrissy's Court]]''\n| rowspan=\"12\" | Unscripted and Docs\n| [[Court show|Arbitration court show]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | April 6, 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|last=Spangler|first=Todd|title=Chrissy Teigen to Rule Over Small-Claims 'Chrissy's Court' in Show for Jeffrey Katzenberg's Quibi|url=https://variety.com/2019/digital/news/chrissy-teigen-court-show-quibi-1203224540|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=May 23, 2019|accessdate=June 21, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Komonibo |first1=Ineye |title=Chrissy Teigen's Court Is Now In Session: Here's A First Look At Her New Show |url=https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2020/03/9496454/chrissys-court-quibi-original-series |website=[[Refinery29]] |accessdate=March 3, 2020 |language=en |date=March 2, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Dishmantled''\n| Cooking competition\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/tituss-burgess-host-cooking-competition-series-dishmantled-chopped-creator-quibi-1202669676/|title=Tituss Burgess To Host Cooking Competition Series 'Dishmantled' From 'Chopped' Creator For Quibi|last1=Petski|first1=Denise|website=Deadline|date=August 16, 2019|access-date=January 13, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''Elba vs. Block''\n| [[Reality television|Reality]]\n| April 13, 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tingley|first1=Anna|title=TV News Roundup: Idris Elba to Star in Car-Stunt Series at Quibi|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/tv-news-roundup-idris-elba-quibi-car-stunt-series-1203242824|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=June 13, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n| ''Gayme Show''\n|rowspan=2| [[Game show]]\n| rowspan=\"9\" | April 6, 2020\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/quibi-gayme-show-comedy-competition-matt-rogers-dave-mizzoni-1202763096/|title=Quibi Sets 'Gayme Show' Comedy Competition With Hosts Matt Rogers And Dave Mizzoni|last=Ramos|first=Dino-Ray|last2=Ramos|first2=Dino-Ray|date=2019-10-17|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-11-12}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''Gone Mental with Lior''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Murder House Flip''\n|rowspan=2| [[Reality television|Reality]]\n| <ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Punk'd]]''\n| <ref name=\"singled-out-punkd\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''The Sauce''\n| Game show\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Singled Out]]''\n| [[Dating game show]]\n|<ref name=\"singled-out-punkd\">{{cite web|title=MTV Studios and Quibi Sign Deal to Reimagine Iconic Franchises \"Punk'd\" and \"Singled Out\" for a Whole New Generation|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/06/04/mtv-studios-and-quibi-sign-deal-to-reimagine-iconic-franchises-punkd-and-singled-out-for-a-whole-new-generation-599301/20190604mtv01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=June 4, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite