734/speedrun-polygon-quibi-launch-announce-jimmy-mondal|title=Polygon's daily news show debuts April 6 on Quibi|last1=de Rochefort|first1=Simone|website=Polygon|date=March 6, 2020|access-date=March 3, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Last Night's Late Night''\n|Entertainment\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''The Daily Chill''\n|Inspiration\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''The Rachel Hollis Show''\n|Inspiration\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Sexology with Shan Boodram''\n|Intimacy\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Fashion's a Drag''\n|Fashion\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''The Nod with Brittany & Eric''\n|Cultural\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Around the World'' by [[BBC News]]\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Morning Report'' by [[NBC News]]\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Evening Report'' by NBC News\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Saturday Report'' by NBC News\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Sunday Report'' by NBC News\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Pulso News'' by [[Telemundo]]\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''For the Cultura'' by Telemundo\n|Pop culture\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Weather Today'' by [[The Weather Channel]]\n|Weather\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''NewsDay'' by [[CTV News]]\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''NewsNight'' by CTV News\n|News\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Sports AM'' by [[The Sports Network|TSN]]\n|Sports\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobilesyrup.com/2020/04/06/mobile-streaming-service-quibi-now-available-canada/|title=Mobile streaming service Quibi now available in Canada|first=Aisha|last=Malik|work=MobileSyrup|date=April 6, 2020|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|''The Replay'' by [[ESPN]]\n|Sports\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''All the Feels'' by the Dodo\n|Inspiration\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Close Up'' by [[E! News]]\n|Entertainment\n|<ref name=\"/Film-90\" />