ies-1203240530|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=June 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|''The Expecting''\n|\n|Horror\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n| ''Frat Boy Genius''\n|\n| [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n|\n|<ref name=\"variety-march-9\" />\n|-\n| ''#FreeRayShawn''\n|Movies in Chapters\n| [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|April 13, 2020\n|<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n| ''How They Made Her''\n|\n| [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|last=Roettgers|first=Janko|title=Katzenberg's Quibi Lines Up New Projects With Catherine Hardwicke, Stephen Curry|url=https://variety.com/2018/digital/news/katzenberg-quibi-hardwicke-curry-1203081100|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 5, 2018|accessdate=June 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|''The Last American Vampire''\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Spielberg's After Dark]]''\n|\n| [[Horror fiction|Horror]]\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Schneider|first1=Michael|last2=Schneider|first2=Michael|title=Steven Spielberg Writing Horror Series for Quibi That You Can Only Watch at Night|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/steven-spielberg-quibi-jeffrey-katzenberg-horror-1203237395|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=June 10, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Swimming with Sharks''\n|\n| rowspan=\"6\" |[[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]]\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''The Stranger''\n|Movies in Chapters\n|April 13, 2020\n|<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/veena-sud-quibi-the-stranger-series-1202649422/|title=Veena Sud Sets Thriller Series 'The Stranger' At Quibi|first1=Erik|last1=Pedersen|first2=Erik|last2=Pedersen|date=July 19, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n|''Toys''\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''Transmissions''\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''Wireless''\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n| ''Wolves and Villagers''\n|\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|