neye |title=Chrissy Teigen's Court Is Now In Session: Here's A First Look At Her New Show |url=https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2020/03/9496454/chrissys-court-quibi-original-series |website=[[Refinery29]] |accessdate=March 3, 2020 |language=en |date=March 2, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Dishmantled''\n| Cooking competition\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/tituss-burgess-host-cooking-competition-series-dishmantled-chopped-creator-quibi-1202669676/|title=Tituss Burgess To Host Cooking Competition Series 'Dishmantled' From 'Chopped' Creator For Quibi|last1=Petski|first1=Denise|website=Deadline|date=August 16, 2019|access-date=January 13, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''Elba vs. Block''\n| [[Reality television|Reality]]\n| April 13, 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tingley|first1=Anna|title=TV News Roundup: Idris Elba to Star in Car-Stunt Series at Quibi|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/tv-news-roundup-idris-elba-quibi-car-stunt-series-1203242824|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=June 13, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"April/Film\" />\n|-\n| ''Gayme Show''\n|rowspan=2| [[Game show]]\n| rowspan=\"9\" | April 6, 2020\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/quibi-gayme-show-comedy-competition-matt-rogers-dave-mizzoni-1202763096/|title=Quibi Sets 'Gayme Show' Comedy Competition With Hosts Matt Rogers And Dave Mizzoni|last=Ramos|first=Dino-Ray|last2=Ramos|first2=Dino-Ray|date=2019-10-17|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-11-12}}</ref><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''Gone Mental with Lior''\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n|''Murder House Flip''\n|rowspan=2| [[Reality television|Reality]]\n| <ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Punk'd]]''\n| <ref name=\"singled-out-punkd\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''The Sauce''\n| Game show\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" /><ref name=\"/Film-90\" />\n|-\n| ''[[Singled Out]]''\n| [[Dating game show]]\n|<ref name=\"singled-out-punkd