ice One!' With Ron Funches|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/quibi-comedy-game-show-nice-one-ron-funches-1202771003/|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=October 28, 2019|accessdate=October 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Pillow Talk with Demi Lovato''\n|\n|Talk show\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''Pranks''\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''Potty Talk''\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|''Q-Talks''\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|Untitled Scooter Braun dance competition\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|}\n\n===News===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n!Category\n! Genre\n! Premiere\n! Notes\n|-\n| ''Daily Essentials''\n|\n| News/[[Sports]]\n| April 2020\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=ESPN to Serve as the Exclusive U.S. Multi-Sport Content Provider for Quibi's Daily Essentials|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/10/07/espn-to-serve-as-the-exclusive-us-multi-sport-content-provider-for-quibis-daily-essentials-730412/20191007espn01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=October 7, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/streaming-startup-quibi-to-create-daily-news-show-with-nbc-11563249780|title=Streaming Startup Quibi to Create Daily News Show With NBC|last=Mullin|first=Benjamin|website=WSJ|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''The Drop''\n|\n| Music\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/quibi-hip-hop-news-daily-essentials-gunpowder-and-sky-complex-1202767589/|title=Quibi Adds Hip-Hop News Show From Gunpowder & Sky, Complex And Den Of Thieves To Daily Essentials Slate|last1=Hipes|first1=Patrick|website=Deadline|date=October 23, 2019|access-date=January 13, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|''This Day in Useless Celebrity History''\n|\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\" />\n|-\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"vineyard-nyt\">{{cite web |last1=Vineyard |first1=Jennifer |title=Quibi Is Coming. Here Are the Famous People Making Shows for It. |url=htt